      {
        "experiment_id": 1,
        "reaction_type": "羟醛缩合反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Aldol condensation reaction",
        "description": "在MgAl混合氧化物催化剂上，进行糠醛和2-丁酮的羟醛缩合反应，以选择性合成具有支链结构的C9 α,β-不饱和羰基化合物（生物航煤前体）。优化了反应条件（催化剂Mg/Al原子比、反应时间、反应物摩尔比、催化剂负载量、反应温度）。",
        "text_snippet": "The aldol condensation of furfural with 2-butanone was performed in an 80 mL stainless-steel autoclave... The most suitable catalyst, contributing the highest furfural conversion (63%) and selectivity of the branched-chain C9 products (77%), is LDO3... The suitable reaction conditions to produce the branched-chain C9 ketones are 1:5 furfural:2-butanone molar ratio, 5 wt.% catalyst loading, 120 °C reaction temperature, and 8 h reaction time.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Aldol condensation reaction"
      }
    ]
  },
